{% load static %}

<html lang="en">
  <head>

    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

  <body>
  <div class="logo"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sojibbuet109"><img src="data:image/png;base64,"></a>

          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sojibbuet109">
       <img src="{% static 'image/rod.jpg' %}"></a><br><br><br><br><br><br>

          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sojibbuet109/videos/1365437803639470">
       <img src="{% static 'image/rod.jpg' %}"></a>

            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BiVyN2ftrrs">
       <img src="{% static 'image/mama.jpg' %}"></a>

            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RM_kk0sZw6Q">
       <img src="{% static 'image/me.jpg' %}"></a>

<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
           <a href="../other/">
       <img src="{% static 'image/apple.jpg' %}"></a>

          <a href="../math/">
               <img src="{% static 'image/orange.jpg' %}"></a>


          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W2-Hey75y7U">
          <img src="{% static 'image/apple.jpg '%}"> </a>



      <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">



  <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">calculator app</a>
  <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
  </button>

  <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
    <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">

      <li class="nav-item"> <!-- item 1 -->
        <a class="nav-link" href="#about">about</a>
      </li>


        <li class="nav-item"> <!-- item 2 -->
        <a class="nav-link" href="#instructions">instructions</a>
        </li>

    </ul>

  </div>
</nav>



   <div class="container-fluid" style="margin-bottom 20rem;">

       {% if error %}

        <div class="row">


           <div class="col-md-6" style="margin:0 auto;">

               <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                 <strong>sorry error is find</strong>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
               </button>
           </div>

           </div>
        </div>

               {% endif %}


              {% if result%}

                <div class="row">

                    <div class="col-md-6" style="margin:0 auto;">


               <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                 <strong> {{q}}={{ans}} </strong>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
               </button>
               </div>



                 </div>
                </div>


               {% endif %}

       </div>




       <div class="row">
           <div class="col-md-6" style="margin:1rem auto 0 auto;">
               
               <img class="img-fluid" src="{% static 'image/math.jpg' %}">
               <img class="img-fluid" src="{% static 'image/math2.jpg' %}">

               <div class="card">
                   <div class="card-body">

                       <form method="GET" action="{% url 'submitquery' %}">

                           <div class="form-group">
                               <input type="search" class="form-control" name="query" id="query">
                           </div>

                           <input type="submit" class="btn btn-success">

                            <input type="reset" class="btn btn-danger">


                       </form>

                   </div>
               </div>
           </div>
       </div>


      <div class="row"> <!-- about block -->
           <div class="col-md-6" style="margin:2rem auto 0 auto;">

               <p class="display-4" id="about" name="about"  style="text-align:center;">
                 about
               </p>


               <p class="lead bg-success text-white" style="text-align:center;">
                we want to calculate in this website
               </p>
              



           </div>
      </div>



       <!-- instructions block -->
            <div class="row"> <!-- about block -->
           <div class="col-md-6" style="margin:2rem auto 0 auto;">

               <p class="display-4" id="instructions" name="instructions"  style="text-align:center;">
                 instructions
               </p>


                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item">+ addition</li>
                      <li class="list-group-item">- minus</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">* multiplication</li>
                   <li class="list-group-item">/ division</li>
                  <li class="list-group-item">// floor division</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">() parenthesis</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">** exponential</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">% mod</li>
                 </ul>


               <p class="lead" style="text-align:center;">
                 all instructions here ok
               </p>
           </div>
      </div>


   </div>


   <div class="container-fluid" style="background:black;">
       <div class="row">
           <footer class="fixed-bottom navbar-light ">
               <p>
                   footer
               </p>
           </footer>

       </div>
   </div>

    <!-- Optional JavaScript -->

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</html>
